snippet.title: Clone Hero v1.0
snippet.description:
DOWNLOAD CLONE HERO V1 NOW: https://clonehero.net 

After 3 years of development and dozens of Public Test Builds, Clone Hero V1 is finally here! There’s plenty of new features and customization options that made their way into the game since V0.23.

https://clonehero.net/2022/11/29/v1-release.html

A HUGE shoutout and thank-you to the public testers who sent in their color profiles! Below is a list of file-names and their creators, including those not featured in the video, you can download them here: https://tinyurl.com/color-profiles
They go in the `Custom\Colors` folder in your Clone Hero files.


3-UP : 3-UP                  
HUESHIFT_HERO : KanaiZo               
jdurandTV_FADE : jdurandTV + Storm VI (+ custom highway jdurand.png)
tomato : Makis Thicc           
LB_purple : NyQuil                
blue_to_pink_rainbow : thardwardy            
Red-And-White : Zacco                 
Crashy_Colors_Definitive_Edition : Crashy                
MilkAndHoneyAndUranium : OrangeHat             
purple_fun : Davidopathy           
TransFlag : BeatriceGH (+ custom highway TransTrans.png)
ralsei : killicus1103          
Eye_Candy_by_Just_Jenny : Just Jenny            
EternalBlueFade : YoltsOJ               
vibrant_vanilla : daandroid614          
astrogirl : Yorak                 
kat : kattny                
MetalHeroCH : MetalHeroCH
   
Follow us!

Discord: https://discord.gg/Hsn4Cgu
Twitter: https://twitter.com/CloneHero
Reddit: https://www.reddit.com/r/CloneHero/
